    %section.row-content
      %article.row-content-single.row-content-bottom
        %div
          %h2.row-title Awesome partners, lovely organizers
          %p 48rails is built with the help of many technical, logistic and media partners. 

          %p 
            The hackathon is brought to you by some lovely folks from programmers in padua &mdash; you can reach us at 
            %a{href: 'mailto:ninja@48rails.it'} ninja@48rails.it
      %article.row-content-double
        %ul
          %li.hackathon-partners-and-organizers-square
            %a{href: 'http://rubyitalia.teamartist.com/', target: '_blank', title: 'Associazione Ruby Italia'}
              = image_tag 'logos/ruby-it.jpg'
